# Nutrition App — Educational demo

## Setup
1. Make sure you have Node.js (>=14) installed.
2. In the project folder run:
   npm install

3. Put a hero image at `public/images/nutrition.jpg`. Recommended: 1200×600 or similar.

4. Start the server:
   npm start

5. Open http://localhost:3000 in your browser.

The server will create `nutrition.db` automatically.

## Notes
- This site provides educational nutrition information only. Not medical advice.
- Submissions stored in SQLite are non-sensitive (optional name + non-medical choices). For production, add authentication, HTTPS, input validations and privacy policies.
